# License

This repository contains multiple licenses depending on the component.

## FFmpeg Binaries

FFmpeg itself is licensed under LGPL/GPL. The prebuilt binaries in this project
inherit licenses from the codecs they include:

| Package | Codecs Included | License |
|---------|-----------------|---------|
| `@pproenca/ffmpeg` | VP8/9, AV1, Opus, Vorbis, MP3 | LGPL-2.1-or-later |
| `@pproenca/ffmpeg-non-free` | All above + H.264/H.265 (x264/x265) | GPL-2.0-or-later |

The main `@pproenca/ffmpeg` package is safe for commercial use with LGPL compliance.
Use `@pproenca/ffmpeg-non-free` only if your project is GPL-compatible.

See `npm/*/package.json` for specific package licenses.

