## Third-Party Licenses

This project builds the following open-source libraries. Their licenses apply
to the respective portions of the built binaries:

- FFmpeg: LGPL-2.1+ / GPL-2.0+ (https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html)
- libvpx: BSD-3-Clause
- aom (AV1): BSD-2-Clause
- dav1d: BSD-2-Clause
- SVT-AV1: BSD-2-Clause-Patent
- Opus: BSD-3-Clause
- Ogg/Vorbis: BSD-3-Clause
- LAME: LGPL-2.0+
- x264: GPL-2.0+
- x265: GPL-2.0+
